</div>


				<div style="width: 70%;" class="figure-inner">
						<a class="lightbox" href="/img/figure/figure12_9.jpg" data-title='Figure 12.9 Social, Ecological, and Technological Components of Infrastructure'>
							<picture>
		<source media="(min-width: 1200px)" srcset="/img/styles/figure12_9-1200.jpg, /img/styles/figure12_9-1200@2x.jpg 2x">
